  <entry>
    <title>高强度密码生成器 - OnePassJs</title>
    <link href="/blog/2024/onepassjs/"/>
    <url>/blog/2024/onepassjs/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<div>    <label for="param1">记忆密码：</label>    <input type="password" id="param1" oninput="testEncrypt()"> </div><div>    <label for="param2">区分代号：</label>    <input type="text" id="param2" oninput="testEncrypt()"></div><div>    <label for="specialChars">包含特殊符号：</label>    <input type="checkbox" id="specialChars" checked="true" onchange="testEncrypt()"></div><div>    <label for="capitalizeFirst">首位大写：</label>    <input type="checkbox" id="capitalizeFirst" checked="true" onchange="testEncrypt()"></div><div>    <label for="passwordLength">密码长度（6-32位）：</label>    <input type="range" id="passwordLength" min="6" max="32" value="16" oninput="testEncrypt()">    <output id="lengthDisplay">16</output></div><div>    <label for="generatedPassword">生成的密码：</label>    <textarea id="generatedPassword" readonly row=1 col=34 style="width: 42ch; height: 4ex; resize: none;"></textarea>    <button class="iconfont icon-cliplist" title="复制密码" onclick="copyToClipboard()"></div><div>    <input type="checkbox" id="savePassword" onchange="savePasswordChange()">    <label for="savePassword">保存记忆密码（浏览器明文保存）</label></div><script src="/zhider-hexo/wasm/onepass.js" type="text/javascript"></script><script>    let willSavePwd = () => { return document.getElementById('savePassword').checked; }    async function testEncrypt() {        // 在这里编写处理逻辑，根据输入和选项生成并显示密码        const param1 = document.getElementById('param1').value;        const param2 = document.getElementById('param2').value;        const specialCharsEnabled = document.getElementById('specialChars').checked;        const capitalizeFirst = document.getElementById('capitalizeFirst').checked;        const passwordLength = parseInt(document.getElementById('passwordLength').value, 10);        document.getElementById("lengthDisplay").value = passwordLength;        // 输入框一个是空就不生成        if (!param1 || !param2) {            return;        }        // ... 实现密码生成的代码 ...        if (willSavePwd()) { localStorage.setItem('onepassjs_pwd', param1); }        let generatedPassword = await encrypt(param1, param2, specialCharsEnabled, capitalizeFirst, passwordLength); // 用实际生成的密码替换此处        document.getElementById('generatedPassword').textContent = generatedPassword;    }    function copyToClipboard() {        document.getElementById('generatedPassword').select();        document.execCommand('copy');    }    function savePasswordChange() {        if (willSavePwd()) {            // 保存记忆密码            let param1 = document.getElementById('param1').value;            localStorage.setItem('onepassjs_pwd', param1);        } else {            // 删除保存的记忆密码            localStorage.removeItem('onepassjs_pwd');        }    }    // 如果有保存记忆密码，就读取    let savedPwd = localStorage.getItem('onepassjs_pwd');    document.getElementById('savePassword').checked = !!savedPwd;    if (savedPwd) {        document.getElementById('param1').value = savedPwd;    } </script><blockquote><p>密码生成完全在本地运行，没有网络交互，也不会储存到本地。由浏览器提供 Crypto API 进行计算。<br>代码行为完全和 <a href="https://github.com/kaku2015/OnePassWindows">https://github.com/kaku2015/OnePassWindows</a> 相同。</p></blockquote>]]></content>
    
    
